verbose_text: Furthermore, the ability of goblin1 to inhibit O GlcNAcylation of a well characterized human substrate protein, TAB1 [XREF_BIBR], was investigated by Western blotting employing a TAB1 O-GlcNAc Ser 395 site specific antibody (XREF_FIG D, and Supplementary Figure S2 at http://www.biochemj.org/bj/457/bj4570497add.htm).
